Gentoo packaging
================

Gentoo builds run directly on the host via genkernel — no Docker container.
The build logic lives in scripts/lib/build-gentoo.sh and
scripts/lib/install-gentoo.sh.

If a Gentoo ebuild is desired in the future, place it here:
- linux-liquorix-<version>.ebuild

Reference: https://github.com/GKernelCI/gentoo-sources-build
